1373
01:39:31.924 --> 01:39:34.051
<i>My name is Joel Dawson.</i>

1374
01:39:34.135 --> 01:39:38.222
<i>I'm 24 years old. and I survived
seven days on the surface.</i>

1375
01:39:46.481 --> 01:39:47.899
