Go. Live your life.</i>

1398
01:41:20.783 --> 01:41:23.828
<i>It won't be easy.
but it'll be worth it.</i>

1399
01:41:25.746 --> 01:41:29.959
<i>I traveled 85 miles to find what I had
been missing below ground for seven years</i>

1400
01:41:30.042 --> 01:41:32.461
<i>was right above my
head this whole time.</i>

1401
01:41:32.545 --> 01:41:34.171
<i>And it's incredible.</i>

1402
01:41:35.464 --> 01:41:38.551
<i>And one last thing.
Don't settle.</i>

1403
01:41:38.634 --> 01:41:42.305
<i>You don't have to. Not even
at the end of the world.</i>

1404
01:41:50.396 --> 01:41:52.148
<i>Signing off.</i>

1405
01:41:52.231 --> 01:41:53.899
<i>Joel Dawson.</i>

1406
01:42:22.637 --> 01:42:25.306
